def julian_day_of_week(day, month, year):
    a = (14 - month) / 12
    y = year + 4800 - a
    m = month + 12 * a - 3
    jdn = day + (153 * m + 2) // 5 + 365 * y + y // 4 - 32083
    return (jdn + 1) % 7
